  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Bentiu Community Trauma Awareness and Psychosocial Support Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Reduced Trauma effects among the community members in Bentiu through the project intervention to enhance mental health and Psychosocial Support among the survivors of GBV and torture victims in the community.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">a. Creation of Community PSS centers
b. Creation of Trauma healing therapy theatres
c. Identification of the victims of torture
d. Identification of the survivors of S/GBV
e. Documentation of the cases identified 
f. Psychosocial support services 
g. Trauma healing therapy services
h. Training on Entrepreneurships
I. Training of women on peer support
j. Training of 60 Community-based Volunteers
k. Facilitation of the community based Volunteers</narrative>
  </description>
